** '''Radimus Erkle:''' Taken one too many hits to the noggin, have you? Here's what I want you to do. 
** '''Radimus Erkle:'''  You need to find a way into the Kharazi Jungle. 
** '''Radimus Erkle:'''  Then you need to explore and map the three areas I asked you to.
** '''Radimus Erkle:''' While you're there you need to make contact with the Kharazi tribe and establish friendly relations. 
** '''Radimus Erkle:'''  As proof of all this, I want you to bring back the completed map and a token of the Kharazi's esteem - something we can put on display. 
** '''Radimus Erkle:''' Did you get all that?
